snippet.title: Combo Card Clashers - Dev Log #2: Tutorial Video Update | PC
snippet.description:
Link to Game:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2054770/Combo_Card_Clashers/

Hang out with the discord community:
https://discord.gg/BjVTtPGZfD

Hey guys,
Showing my WIP of my new tutorial for Combo Card Clashers. This will be included in the next update! This will make the game accessible for new players who are unfamiliar to the genre and experienced players alike! I hope you enjoy it. I will try to upload more in the future.
